<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p><span><strong>福州市中国农民丰收节主场活动</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong>将于</strong></span><span><strong>本月27日在罗源县松山镇举办</strong></span><span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200922/5589a6e0d15e48259468bf31b9c8d243.jpeg" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>为庆祝难得可贵的丰收佳节</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>福州各区县早已忙活开了</span></p>
